{
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "sceneId": "cafeteria-buzz",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "cb-1",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Okay okay okay— so my mom said yes to the bonfire thing. No for real.",
          "emotion": "buzzing",
          "action": "touches Sol's arm"
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-2",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "String lights, my uncle's speaker system, skate bowl by the reservoir. Best thing that's happened to this grade all year."
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-3",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "It's happening. Obviously.",
          "action": "doesn't look up from her phone, Notes app open"
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-4",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "I already have a list going."
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-5",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "A list? For a hangout?"
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-6",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Everything's a hangout until forty people show up and there's no music and someone's mom calls the cops. I plan. It's a service."
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-7",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "She's not wrong. Saved my last party from actual chaos.",
          "emotion": "laughing half-second early"
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-8",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "This is nice. Being the one people just assume is already coming."
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-9",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "So you're in, right? Obviously you're in—"
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-10",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Obviously I'm in."
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-11",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Good.",
          "action": "small smile, typing",
          "emotion": "satisfied"
        },
        {
          "id": "cb-12",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "One less name to think about."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "guest-list-tease",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "glt-1",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Okay so— forty. We're capping it at forty.",
          "action": "reading off her phone"
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-2",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Obviously. Can't invite the whole zip code."
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-3",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Forty's still like, a third of the grade—",
          "emotion": "laughing"
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-4",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Forty's generous.",
          "pause": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-5",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "You should see who I cut.",
          "action": "eyes flick across the cafeteria for half a second, then back"
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-6",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Some people just don't really fit the vibe, you know? No offense to anyone."
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-7",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Okay but anyway— we need a playlist that's not just Priya's workout mix—",
          "action": "quick reframe, busy with his tray"
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-8",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "It got you through indoor track, Jordan.",
          "emotion": "flat"
        },
        {
          "id": "glt-9",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "She didn't say a name. She didn't have to."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "priya-pushback",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "pp-1",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Since when is Alex your business, Sol?",
          "emotion": "eyebrow up, testing not hostile"
        },
        {
          "id": "pp-2",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Okay— no for real, can we not do this right before my party planning—",
          "action": "suddenly very busy with his tray"
        },
        {
          "id": "pp-3",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "I'm not being mean. I'm being efficient. There's a difference.",
          "pause": 400
        },
        {
          "id": "pp-4",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "You've talked to them, what, twice?"
        },
        {
          "id": "pp-5",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "Twice. She's not wrong. So why does this feel like it matters more than twice?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "easy-comfort",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "ec-1",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "—and that's why we're never letting Priya near the aux cord again—",
          "emotion": "laughing"
        },
        {
          "id": "ec-2",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "It was one time. The bass was, objectively, incredible.",
          "emotion": "deadpan"
        },
        {
          "id": "ec-3",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The table laughs. Sol laughs a half-second late, same as always."
        },
        {
          "id": "ec-4",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Across the room, Alex looks up at the sound of it — just for a second — then goes back to their sketchbook, like they didn't."
        },
        {
          "id": "ec-5",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "I didn't even notice them sitting over there. Since when do I not notice that."
        },
        {
          "id": "ec-6",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Anyway— you're definitely coming, right? Obviously—",
          "action": "touches Sol's arm"
        },
        {
          "id": "ec-7",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Obviously."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "quiet-deflection",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "qd-1",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Oh my god, thank you, yes— okay, no top 40 garbage, I have opinions—",
          "action": "already typing"
        },
        {
          "id": "qd-2",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "She has a seventeen-song draft already. I've seen it.",
          "emotion": "laughing"
        },
        {
          "id": "qd-3",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "It's called preparation, Jordan."
        },
        {
          "id": "qd-4",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Okay, so, opening song. This matters more than people think."
        },
        {
          "id": "qd-5",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "Nothing happened. Nothing got decided. The list's still the list."
        },
        {
          "id": "qd-6",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Okay but for real, you're coming right?"
        },
        {
          "id": "qd-7",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Wouldn't miss it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "guilty-lunch",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "gl-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Lunch winds down. Trays scrape, chairs squeak back."
        },
        {
          "id": "gl-2",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Okay but for real, forty people, string lights, this is gonna be the best thing that's happened to eighth grade—",
          "action": "mouth full, cheerful"
        },
        {
          "id": "gl-3",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Obviously.",
          "action": "checking her phone"
        },
        {
          "id": "gl-4",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Across the room, Alex buses their tray alone and slips out the side door — quiet, quick, the way they used to before the project."
        },
        {
          "id": "gl-5",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "Nobody else even looked up."
        },
        {
          "id": "gl-6",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Sol? You good?"
        },
        {
          "id": "gl-7",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Yeah. Just— yeah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "find-alex",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "fa-1",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Hey— Alex, wait up."
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-2",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "...Hey.",
          "action": "stopping, adjusting sketchbook under their arm",
          "emotion": "guarded"
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "So, um. Jordan's doing this thing Friday. Birthday hangout, skate bowl by the reservoir. You should come."
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-4",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Since when do I get invited to swim-bro pool parties?",
          "emotion": "flat, half-joke"
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-5",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "It's not— there's no pool. It's a bonfire."
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-6",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "And I'm inviting you. Not Jordan. Me."
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-7",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "...Priya know about this?",
          "action": "studying her, guard still up"
        },
        {
          "id": "fa-8",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "There it is."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "hallway-check-in",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "hci-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Days pass. Lunches. Hallway nods. Nothing said out loud."
        },
        {
          "id": "hci-2",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Hey. Wasn't sure if you'd still be here."
        },
        {
          "id": "hci-3",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Wow. Checking on me. Big day.",
          "action": "not looking up from their locker"
        },
        {
          "id": "hci-4",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "I'm allowed to check on people.",
          "emotion": "small laugh"
        },
        {
          "id": "hci-5",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "You didn't, though. Not at lunch.",
          "action": "closing locker"
        },
        {
          "id": "hci-6",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Kind of a long week to just now notice."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "skip-to-project-class",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "spc-1",
          "character": "ms-chen",
          "text": "Sol, Alex. Five minutes. Progress check.",
          "action": "clipboard, no negotiation"
        },
        {
          "id": "spc-2",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "We're on schedule. Panels three through six are inked.",
          "emotion": "polite, closed off"
        },
        {
          "id": "spc-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Yeah, it's— it's looking really good."
        },
        {
          "id": "spc-4",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Thanks.",
          "action": "not looking up"
        },
        {
          "id": "spc-5",
          "character": "ms-chen",
          "text": "...That's five minutes.",
          "action": "writes something small in the margins, doesn't say it out loud",
          "pause": 1000
        },
        {
          "id": "spc-6",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "A week ago we were arguing about panel layouts for twenty minutes. Now it's 'thanks.' I did that."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "alex-warms",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "aw-1",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Hey. Wait.",
          "action": "catching up to her, which is unusual"
        },
        {
          "id": "aw-2",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "I'm not saying yes.",
          "pause": 400
        },
        {
          "id": "aw-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Okay."
        },
        {
          "id": "aw-4",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "But I'm not saying no either.",
          "action": "shrug, looking away",
          "emotion": "guarded"
        },
        {
          "id": "aw-5",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Maybe."
        },
        {
          "id": "aw-6",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Maybe's good. I'll take maybe.",
          "emotion": "small smile"
        },
        {
          "id": "aw-7",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Don't get used to it.",
          "emotion": "almost a real laugh"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "alex-unsure",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "au-1",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "I said I'd think about it.",
          "pause": 400
        },
        {
          "id": "au-2",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "I'm still thinking."
        },
        {
          "id": "au-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "That's fair."
        },
        {
          "id": "au-4",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Is it weird that I don't know if that's a nice thing you're doing, or a— I don't know. A thing.",
          "emotion": "guarded"
        },
        {
          "id": "au-5",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "It's not a thing. I just want you there."
        },
        {
          "id": "au-6",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "...We'll see.",
          "emotion": "quiet, unconvinced but not closed"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "alex-declines-firmly",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "adf-1",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "I'm good. Really.",
          "pause": 400
        },
        {
          "id": "adf-2",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "You don't have to keep asking."
        },
        {
          "id": "adf-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "I know. I just—"
        },
        {
          "id": "adf-4",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "It's a lot of birthday party for someone who's talked to me twice.",
          "emotion": "not unkind, just tired"
        },
        {
          "id": "adf-5",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "...Yeah. Okay.",
          "emotion": "quiet"
        },
        {
          "id": "adf-6",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Thanks, though. For asking twice.",
          "emotion": "softer, almost gentle"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "party-day-together",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "pdt-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "String lights. Bonfire. Half the grade laughing too loud. Alex hovers at the edge, skateboard under one arm like an exit strategy."
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-2",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "You came! No for real, this is great—",
          "action": "waving them over, touching their shoulder"
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-3",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Yeah. Wasn't doing anything else.",
          "emotion": "flat"
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-4",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "—and that's the story of how Jordan almost set his own eyebrows on fire, very on brand—",
          "action": "mid-story to the group"
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-5",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "—careful, Sketchbook, don't reenact it over there.",
          "action": "glancing at Alex's skateboard"
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-6",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "A few people laugh before they even understand it."
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-7",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "",
          "action": "jaw tight, says nothing"
        },
        {
          "id": "pdt-8",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "There it is."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "party-day-tense",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "pdte-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Alex stands near the drink table, arms crossed, like they're still deciding whether coming was a mistake."
        },
        {
          "id": "pdte-2",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Didn't know they let skateboards at bonfires.",
          "action": "walking past, half habit half test"
        },
        {
          "id": "pdte-3",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Cute look, though."
        },
        {
          "id": "pdte-4",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "A few heads turn to see how Sol reacts."
        },
        {
          "id": "pdte-5",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "Okay. Okay. Say something."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "party-day-absent",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "pda-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The bonfire crackles. String lights sway. It's exactly the party Jordan promised."
        },
        {
          "id": "pda-2",
          "character": "jordan",
          "text": "Okay, no for real, tell me this isn't the best night of eighth grade—",
          "action": "grinning, arm sweep"
        },
        {
          "id": "pda-3",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "Forty-two people. I'm choosing to see that as a win, not a math error.",
          "action": "checking her phone, satisfied"
        },
        {
          "id": "pda-4",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Sol glances at the entrance. Again."
        },
        {
          "id": "pda-5",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "They're not coming. I knew that. I still keep looking."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "ending-quiet-strength",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "eqs-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The fire's dying down to embers. Most people have drifted toward their rides."
        },
        {
          "id": "eqs-2",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "...You didn't have to do that, you know.",
          "action": "arms crossed, looking at the fire, not quite at Sol"
        },
        {
          "id": "eqs-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "I know."
        },
        {
          "id": "eqs-4",
          "character": "priya",
          "text": "It was still—",
          "pause": 600,
          "action": "stops, doesn't finish, gives a small, real nod instead"
        },
        {
          "id": "eqs-5",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "...You stayed.",
          "action": "standing near Sol, quiet"
        },
        {
          "id": "eqs-6",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Yeah."
        },
        {
          "id": "eqs-7",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "Okay.",
          "action": "looking at the fire, something easier in it now"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "ending-balanced-growth",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "ebg-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Walking home, the party noise fading behind them."
        },
        {
          "id": "ebg-2",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "That was... a lot.",
          "action": "kicking their skateboard along"
        },
        {
          "id": "ebg-3",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "Yeah. Sorry it got weird."
        },
        {
          "id": "ebg-4",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "It's not, like, fixed. Just so you know.",
          "action": "shrug"
        },
        {
          "id": "ebg-5",
          "character": "player",
          "text": "I know."
        },
        {
          "id": "ebg-6",
          "character": "alex",
          "text": "...But you showed up. That's something.",
          "action": "glancing at her, almost surprised she's still there"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "ending-comfortable-fit",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "ecf-1",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The walk home is quiet. The party noise fades block by block."
        },
        {
          "id": "ecf-2",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "It was a good night. Exactly the night I wanted."
        },
        {
          "id": "ecf-3",
          "character": "INTERNAL",
          "text": "So why does it feel like I'm carrying something I didn't pick up?"
        },
        {
          "id": "ecf-4",
          "character": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "Somewhere behind her, the reservoir goes dark and quiet, string lights off for the night."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "choiceDialogue": [
    {
      "choiceId": "choice-1",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "speak-up",
          "text": "Maybe Alex should actually be on that list."
        },
        {
          "id": "laugh-along",
          "text": "Ha— brutal. Fair, though."
        },
        {
          "id": "change-subject",
          "text": "Okay wait, what's the playlist looking like?"
        }
      ],
      "responseDialogue": {
        "speak-up": [
          {
            "id": "r-su-1",
            "character": "priya",
            "text": "...Excuse me?",
            "action": "eyebrow raised, half-beat pause"
          },
          {
            "id": "r-su-2",
            "character": "jordan",
            "text": "Okay— no for real, let's not—",
            "action": "already reaching for his phone"
          }
        ],
        "laugh-along": [
          {
            "id": "r-la-1",
            "character": "jordan",
            "text": "See, Sol gets it—",
            "emotion": "relieved, laughing half-second before it lands"
          },
          {
            "id": "r-la-2",
            "character": "priya",
            "text": "Obviously.",
            "action": "small approving smile"
          }
        ],
        "change-subject": [
          {
            "id": "r-cs-1",
            "character": "priya",
            "text": "Oh my god, thank you, yes, okay—",
            "action": "already pulling up a new note"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "choiceId": "choice-2",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "hold-ground",
          "text": "I just think it'd be nice, that's all."
        },
        {
          "id": "back-off",
          "text": "Whatever. Forget it. It's your party."
        }
      ],
      "responseDialogue": {
        "hold-ground": [
          {
            "id": "r-hg-1",
            "character": "priya",
            "text": "Noted.",
            "emotion": "flat, unimpressed",
            "action": "typing again"
          },
          {
            "id": "r-hg-2",
            "character": "priya",
            "text": "Anyway."
          },
          {
            "id": "r-hg-3",
            "character": "jordan",
            "text": "Okay! Great! Nobody's fighting! Love that for us—",
            "emotion": "relieved exhale"
          }
        ],
        "back-off": [
          {
            "id": "r-bo-1",
            "character": "priya",
            "text": "Thank you.",
            "emotion": "satisfied, already moving on"
          },
          {
            "id": "r-bo-2",
            "character": "jordan",
            "text": "Okay but anyway— bonfire. Focus, people—",
            "emotion": "too quickly"
          },
          {
            "id": "r-bo-3",
            "character": "INTERNAL",
            "text": "That was easier than it should've been."
